PERU • adult ♂ ; Departamento de Huánuco , Puerto Inca Province , El Sira Communal Reserve , Campamento Hospital (on the trail to the top of El Sira Communal Reserve); 9.478667° S , 74.778139° W ;
757 m a.s.l.
